<section class="zym-hero" style="position:relative;min-height:92vh;display:flex;align-items:center;padding-top:72px;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:0;">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506126613408-eca07ce68773?w=1920&q=85" alt="Meditation wellness" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" loading="eager">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(26,26,26,0.7) 0%,rgba(45,90,61,0.55) 50%,rgba(74,124,89,0.3) 100%);"></div>
  </div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;width:100%;max-width:1240px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;color:#fff;">
      <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:0.6875rem;font-weight:700;color:#D4AF37;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:5px;margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
        <span style="width:32px;height:1px;background:#D4AF37;display:block;"></span>
        Bienvenido a tu Buena Vida
      </div>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5.5vw,4.25rem);font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.08;margin-bottom:1.75rem;letter-spacing:-1px;">
        Nutre tu cuerpo,<br><span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D4AF37 0%,#E8C84A 100%);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">alimenta tu alma</span>
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);max-width:500px;margin-bottom:2.75rem;line-height:1.8;font-weight:300;">
        Productos naturales de grado terapeutico, disenados para quienes entienden que el bienestar no es un lujo — es una forma de vivir.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:3.5rem;">
        <a href="/collections/all" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:1rem 2.25rem;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;border-radius:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A7C59 0%,#2D5A3D 100%);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(74,124,89,0.35);text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);">
          Explorar Colecciones
        </a>
        <a href="/pages/about" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:1rem 2.25rem;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:0.8125rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;border-radius:8px;background:transparent;color:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);">
          Nuestra Historia
        </a>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:2.5rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding-top:2rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.625rem;font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-weight:400;">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt" style="color:#D4AF37;font-size:0.875rem;"></i> Pago 100% Seguro
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.625rem;font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-weight:400;">
          <i class="fas fa-truck" style="color:#D4AF37;font-size:0.875rem;"></i> Envio Gratis +$50
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.625rem;font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-weight:400;">
          <i class="fas fa-undo" style="color:#D4AF37;font-size:0.875rem;"></i> Garantia 30 Dias
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Hero Banner",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [ { "name": "Hero Banner" } ]
}
{% endschema %}
